            <p>
<lb corresp="#a1"/><gap reason="plain" quantity="2"/><w><supplied>ś</supplied>w<supplied>ā</supplied>tsi</w><w>pat</w><w>yoktsi</w><w>pat</w><w>kene</w><w>eṣ</w><w>akälyme</w><w>mäskatr-äṃ</w><w>säm</w>
